{"tid":738025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拉完繼續有　九巴2巴士座椅被𠝹爛","createTime":"2018-07-11T08:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T09:33:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"097f414bcddd3cde2b2564d9fd6796cd5ac26a5b","tid":738025,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/photo/bkn-20180711122942851-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180711160540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180711122942851-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180711160540&h=c20e8885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴𠝹櫈狂徒昨日(10日)先後落網，惟𠝹櫈刑毀案仍繼續發生。今午(11日)12時13分，一輛由彩福邨開出的9號路線九巴，返回麼地道尖東廣場巴士總站後，車長發現上層2張座椅遭𠝹爛，於是報警求助，警方正展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n至下午2時許，一輛91M九巴在將軍澳寶林巴士總站，有人發現上層其中一張櫈被𠝹爛，警方到場調查。 <br />\n<br />\n連同今日2宗案件，警方由本月至今，11日內接獲27宗九巴座椅被𠝹爛案。警方於昨日在4個地點拘捕5名男子，包括2名巴基斯坦男子，他們懷疑涉及其中5宗案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/bkn-20180711122942851-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fbkn-20180711122942851-0711_00822_001.html&d=JTRu4UmWOKpqXX3Vlp%2FPATANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=f179be5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/bkn-20180711122942851-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"21965b9b2717f39a385d52328a18666447aece9a","tid":738025,"uid":19990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"針對九巴公司？唔見城巴座位比人介既"},{"pid":"9a444ad5e8cdcaad9ac56f1bb1aa22fd7025b9f1","tid":738025,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"21965b9b2717f39a385d52328a18666447aece9a","tid":738025,"uid":19990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"針對九巴公司？唔見城巴座位比人介既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"城巴多數過海同埋好少<br />\n唔似九巴去邊都有嘛<br />\n新巴都無被人搞"},{"pid":"b3